SIMPLE: farther
RECORDS: 3

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Farther
<hw>Far"ther</hw> <pr>(f⟦aum⟧r"⟦th⟧⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>,
<mord><pos>compar.</pos> of <er>Far</er>.</mord>
<amorph>[<pos>superl.</pos> <adjf>Farthest</adjf>
<pr>(-⟦th⟧⟦ecr⟧st)</pr>. See <er>Further</er>.]</amorph> <ety>[For
<ets>farrer</ets>, OE. <ets>ferrer</ets>, compar. of <ets>far</ets>;
confused with <ets>further</ets>. Cf. <er>Farthest</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>More remote; more distant than something
else.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Tending to a greater distance; beyond a certain
point; additional; further.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Before our <qex>farther</qex> way the fates allow.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let me add a <qex>farther</qex> Truth.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some <qex>farther</qex> change awaits us.</q>
<rj><qau>MIlton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Farther</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Farther
<hw>Far"ther</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>At or to a greater
distance; more remotely; beyond; <as>as, let us rest with what we have,
without looking <ex>farther</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Moreover; by way of progress in treating a subject;
<as>as, <ex>farther</ex>, let us consider the probable
event</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<cs><p><col><b>No farther</b></col>, <cd>(used elliptically for) go no
farther; say no more, etc.</cd>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>It will be dangerous to go on. <qex>No farther</qex> !</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p></cs>

<p><ent>Farther</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Farther
<hw>Far"ther</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To help onward.
<mark>[R.]</mark> See <er>Further</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fartherance</ent>⟦br⟧
